---
title: Bulgogi Chicken Breast Udon Stir-Fry with Green Beans and Sesame Seeds
description: Ready in less than 25 minutes, this Bulgogi Chicken Breast Udon Stir-Fry has it all. A popular Korean condiment, bulgogi sauce has a sweet and smoky flavour, thanks to its mix of black bean puree, brown sugar and pear puree.
